text: Kampong Bakiau (Malay for Bakiau Village) is a village situated in the north- eastern part of Tutong District, Brunei, within the mukim of Kiudang. The incumbent village head is Mohd Taib bin Jaludin, who is also the village head for Kampong Pengkalan Mau. The postcode for Kampong Bakiau is TE1143. == References == Bakiau
